{% block content %}
{{
  case_study_header(
    title='Rate Rebrand',
    tags=['Branding', 'UI/UX']
  )
}}

<section class="hero">
  <img
    draggable="false"
    src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/hero__background.jpg"
    alt="Based on true story" />
</section>

<section class="intro">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          As a rising startup hotshot fintech brand, Rate’s essential brand promise is to always provide better value to their users.
        </p>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          However, the Rate team felt that some internal alignment and brand refocusing was necessary to bring their game to the next level.
        </p>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          And with 2 other product brands under the parent Rate brand with plans to launch more, the issue of brand alignment was crucial.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column intro__right">
        <img
          class="intro__image"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/intro__doodle.png" alt="Rates intro doodle"
          data-aos="fade-up">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="concept">
  <div class="concept__bg"></div>
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column cs-container__column--desktop-only">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <p
          data-aos="fade-up">
          So when they reached out to us, we consulted with them in several initial meetings to understand who they were, how they worked as a team, and their aspirations for the brand. This process helps us to craft brand concepts that are aligned with the team’s motivations.
        </p>
        <img
          class="concept__image"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/concept__image.png" alt="Rate rebranding concept"
          data-aos="fade-up">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-insight">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <img
          draggable="false" src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/project-insight__insight.png" alt="Understanding the motivations of the client brand team is an extremely important part of our brand process. After all, brands are only as strong as the teams that drive them." data-aos="fade-up" class="aos-init aos-animate">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-insight__right">
        <img
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/project-insight__mandate.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="next-steps">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <h2 data-aos="fade-up">
          Next Steps
        </h2>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          We started by dissecting the Rate brand, distilling it down to its essentials.
        </p>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          We quickly realised that for a brand to operate in the online payments/ecommerce space, brand credibility and consumer trust is paramount.
        </p>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          Our challenge was to express this sentiment visually, and in a way that would bring it all home for the Rate team.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <div class="next-steps__image">
          <img
            draggable="false"
            src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/next-steps__image.png"
            alt=""
            data-aos="fade-up" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="the-answer">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column the-answer__left">
        <img
          class="the-answer__nike"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/the-answer__nike.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
        <img class="the-answer__copy"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/the-answer__copy.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column the-answer__right">
        <h2 data-aos="fade-up">
          The Answer?
        </h2>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          A logo system based on the absolute value of truth, the foundation on which consumer trust and brand credibility is built.
        </p>
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          The logo system hinges on creative application of the Rate true mark, a symbol of verification that was first used by ancient Roman merchants.
        </p>
        <img
          class="the-answer__lego"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/the-answer__lego.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="values">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column values__left">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          Having listened closely to our clients, we understood that the Rate brand team comprises highly competent individuals, each possessed by an earnest yearning to build a reputable, aspirational, and sustainable brand.
        </p>
        <img
          class="values__left-1"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/values__left-1.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          Thus, the True mark takes on an additional layer of meaning for the brand team, serving as a focal point for internal alignment of their own values.
        </p>
      </div>
       <div class="col-md cs-container__column values__right">
        <div class="values__wrapper">
          <img
            class="values__right-1"
            draggable="false"
            src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/values__right-1.png"
            alt=""
            data-aos="fade-up"/>
          <img
            class="values__right-2"
            draggable="false"
            src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/values__right-2.png"
            alt=""
            data-aos="fade-up" />
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="logos">
  <div class="logos__wrapper">
    <img
      class="logos__logo"
      draggable="false"
      src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/rate__logo.png"
      alt="" />
  </div>
  <div class="logos__wrapper">
    <img
      class="logos__logo-small"
      draggable="false"
      src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/rate-x__logo.png"
      alt="" />
    <img
      class="logos__logo-small"
      draggable="false"
      src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/rate-s__logo.png"
      alt="" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="flexibility">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column flexibility__left">
        <img
          class="flexibility__bulb"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/flexibility__bulb.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          The power of this logo system lies in its flexibility.
        </p>
        <img
          class="flexibility__focus"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/flexibility__focus.png"
          alt=""
          data-aos="fade-up" />
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          And as a brand motif, adding background texture without being overwhelming.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="collaterals">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <p
          data-aos="fade-up">
          We then expanded upon the usage of the system, demonstrating the breadth of possibilities through collateral design.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column cs-container__column--desktop-only">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <picture
    class="collaterals__image"
    data-aos="fade-up">
    <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/collaterals--mobile.png" alt="">
    <source media="(min-width: 769px)" srcset="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/collaterals--desktop.png" alt="">
    <img draggable="false" src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/collaterals--desktop.png" alt="">
  </picture>
</section>

<section class="final">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column final__title">
        <p
          data-aos="fade-up">
          Rate's finalised family of logos
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-container__row final__bottom">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column cs-container__column--desktop-only"></div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <img
          class="final__logo"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/final__rate.png"
          alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <img
          class="final__logo"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/final__rate-x.png"
          alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <img
          class="final__logo"
          draggable="false"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/rate/final__rate-s.png"
          alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column cs-container__column--desktop-only"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

